{"tid":220160,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"你同意「越樣衰嘅人對其他人嘅樣要求越高」嗎？","createTime":"2017-04-27T18:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T21:17:38.000Z","uid":36383,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c491e50768944eb7b6b48f368c557096cb634405","tid":220160,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:02:38.000Z","msg":"因為自己冇，所以想係另一伴/其他人身上取得。就好似咁，社會上大多數都係男女婚姻，因為女人有男人冇嘅特質，而男人都有女人冇嘅特質。<br />\n<br />\n所以一個越樣衰嘅人對身邊嘅人樣要求就會越高。反而一個ok樣嘅人就會得過且過。<br />\n<br />\n一個樣衰嘅人搵好樣嘅人成本比較低，假設一個醜婦搵 Oppa 輸都係輸塊閪。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/28/020117_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2F020117_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=45c09531&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5be14a526736d2daa425748922fe60dbf8d0b9e","tid":220160,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:04:16.000Z","msg":"第一眼以為你貼我出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad76bf06dfd2ed2651f3c275846f1a8ef438324","tid":220160,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:04:38.000Z","msg":"常仔要求都應該好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b258783cbc34f932fa63807c01e78eb067dc2e","tid":220160,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>常仔要求都應該好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></